        </p>
        
        <p class="about-body">
          Currently, I work at a Google Cloud Partner company in Japan, specializing in <strong>Serverless Application development</strong> (Google Cloud, Firebase, DevOps, IaC, Identifier). My deep interest in software architecture has made me proficient in ensuring quality through DDD and clean architecture principles.
        </p>
        
        <blockquote class="about-quote">
